DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260414T183000
DTSTAMP:20260404T084515Z
UID:eca0f4eeac7e6a19d8d5fd741e0031af@family-events-agent
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:storytime,library,baby,toddler,family,Writing & Poetry
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: OCPL - Rancho Santa Margarita Branch\\nCost: free\\
 nAges: 0-60 months\\nCategory: Storytime\\n\\nPoetry Pioneers\n\nEvery sec
 ond Tuesday of the month\n\n5:30-6:30 PM\n\nDiscover a new appreciation fo
 r poetry in a comfortable but inspiring group setting!\n\nDuring each meet
 ing\, we focus on a suggested poetry theme\, style\, or mood with a brief 
 recital or presentation\, writing time with creative prompts\, and a posit
 ive ‘share and discuss’ time.\n\n          2026 Schedule of Themes:\n\
 n          1/13: “Thresholds”\n\n          2/10: “Reflections”\n\n
           3/10: “Whispers”\n\n          4/14: “Seedlings”\n\n     
      5/12: “Journeys”\n\n          6/9: “Harmonics“\n\n          7
 /14: “Horizons”\n\n          8/11: “Imagination”\n\n          9/8:
  “Illumination”\n\n         10/13: “Shadows”\n\n         11/10: 
 “Memories”\n\n         12/8: “Constellations”\n\n\n\n         Meet
 ings are in the Program Room\, 5:30-6:30 PM.  Writing and discussion promp
 ts will be shared.\\n\\nMore info: https://ocpl.libcal.com/event/15946632
LOCATION:Rancho Santa Margarita\, Rancho Santa Margarita
URL:https://ocpl.libcal.com/event/15946632
