  REAL tasty food from Lebanon.\n\nCooking Activities: 11 am &amp\; 2:30 pm
 \n\n*This is not a cooking class\; we will engage in imaginative play and 
 have an opportunity to enjoy pre-made cooked food\n\n\nAbout the play part
 ner: \nLeah Khoury is a CPA by day and author by night (and lunch breaks 
 and weekends). She loves ducks\, traveling\, and making people smile (in 
 no particular order) and from these loves Benny on the Move was born! ✨
 🐣🌎✈️ \nwww.BennyontheMove.com\nInstagram: @BennyontheMove\n\n\n
 Space is limited! Book your tickets in advance to avoid delays!\n*Member
 s do not require a reservation.\n*Events and dates are subject to change.\
 \n\\nMore info: https://www.pretendcity.org/events/cooking-in-the-city-4/
