DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nCost: Fre
 e\\nAges: 0-60 months\\nCategory: Play & Games\\n\\nPretend City Children
 ’s Museum Good To Go Fair: A FREE Family-Friendly Event! This FREE event
  is perfect for families with children ages 0-5. Enjoy a variety of activi
 ties\, resources\, and services designed to support your child’s develop
 ment and overall well-being.\nTIME: 9 am-1 pm\nPretend City Parking Lot\nR
 ain or Shine\n\nDevelopmental Screenings:\n⦁ Check your child’s develo
 pmental milestones and receive valuable insights into their growth\n⦁ Vi
 sion Screenings: Detect early signs of vision issues to ensure your child
 ’s eyes are healthy.\n⦁ Dental Screenings: Keep your child’s smile b
 right and healthy with a free dental check-up.\n⦁ Social-Emotional Scree
 nings: Assess your child’s emotional well-being and get support for the
 ir mental health.\n⦁ And more!\nWhy Attend?\nEarly Detection: Catch pote
 ntial health concerns early\, allowing for timely intervention and support
 .\nFree Services: Access these important health screenings at no cost to y
 ou.\nExpert Guidance: Receive advice and resources from trained profession
 als to support your child’s development and health.\nPLUS\, your child c
 an earn a FREE ticket to Pretend City by completing 3 Health screenings!\n
 Don’t miss the chance to connect with incredible organizations!\nOur Spo
 nsors: CalOptima Health\, Fairmont Schools\, Hoag\, Orange County Departme
 nt of Education\, PNC Bank\n*The event is free\; please note admission to 
 the museum is not included.\\n\\nMore info: https://www.pretendcity.org/ev
 ents/good-to-go-fair-2/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/good-to-go-fair-2/
