 le in the current theme. Then\, after borrowing and enjoying your selectio
 n\, join us so we can all share what we read! \n\n\n\nContact us with any 
 questions at 949-459-6094 or email ocpl.rsm@occr.ocgov.com\n\n\n\nClick on
  PDF below for the 2026 Schedule of Reading & Discussion Themes.\\n\\nMore
  info: https://ocpl.libcal.com/event/15948592
